sg":"關你咩事.."},{"pid":"b3d1767b5f2e632eb4c450fa70c77a561f3f9290","tid":1143254,"uid":117317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:10:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\">不嬲政治冷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但見住政府咁急推<br />\n就知擺明推香港人去死 想幫人手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想大家都一齊關注下 香港仲有得救嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條（需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 莫需有，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由</span>"},{"pid":"85742211768c8178b0638554faa149bdaa399988","tid":1143254,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba823b089e2a8920c2da01cfae21a91f6f42380","tid":1143254,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6be7d68747e1b857b9f73ae66ec26eaa38c60684","tid":1143254,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b1cb041a98739bc47b43d28a56fcd4ca0c7197","tid":1143254,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"Ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"點解唔同媽媽住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"關你咩事.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"8掛"},{"pid":"9c756b1ebe8291a788ce50b1ddb5284bed1bf891","tid":1143254,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85742211768c8178b0638554faa149bdaa399988","tid":1143254,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba823b089e2a8920c2da01cfae21a91f6f42380","tid":1143254,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":